1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,851
but the most efficient sources of education for most people are nearby colleges and universities.

2
00:00:01,201 --> 00:00:03,491
Education is their business.

3
00:00:04,161 --> 00:00:08,771
If you haven't been to college lately, you're in for some wonderful surprises.

4
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:12,451
You'll be pleased at the wide course offerings available.

5
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:17,010
You'll be even more pleased to discover who goes to school after work.

6
00:00:17,201 --> 00:00:24,851
Not the phonies, but rather really promising persons, many of whom already hold very responsible positions.

7
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:33,650
In one evening class of twenty-five persons I conducted recently, there were an owner of a retail chain of twelve stores,

8
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:39,731
two buyers for a national food chain, four graduate engineers, an Air Force colonel,

9
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:42,451
and several others of similar status.

10
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:52,049
Many people earn degrees in evening programs these days, but the degree, which in the final analysis is only a piece of paper,

11
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:54,291
is not their primary motivation.

12
00:00:54,641 --> 00:01:00,691
They are going to school to build their minds, which is a sure way to invest in a better future.

13
00:01:01,201 --> 00:01:05,731
And make no mistake about this, education is a real bargain.

14
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:11,331
A moderate investment will keep you in school one night each week for a full year.

15
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:16,291
Compute the cost as a percentage of your gross income, and then ask yourself,

16
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,491
isn't my future worth this small investment?

17
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:23,569
Why not make an investment decision right now?

18
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:27,251
Call it school, one night a week for life.

19
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:30,691
It will keep you progressive, young, alert.

20
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:38,530
It will keep you abreast of your areas of interest, and it will surround you with other people who also are going places.

21
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,050
2.

22
00:01:40,241 --> 00:01:40,451
Invest in idea starters.
